            "Transparent documentation for partner verification."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "size-guide": {
      "title": "Size Guide",
      "intro": "Reference charts and simple measuring instructions for rings, bracelets, and necklaces.",
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Ring Sizes",
          "bullets": [
            "Use a paper strip or ring sizer to measure finger circumference.",
            "Match Indian sizes to international equivalents before finalizing MTO submissions."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Jewellery Lengths",
          "bullets": [
            "Bracelets should sit comfortably with a half-inch allowance.",
            "Necklace lengths should be chosen according to neckline, pendant weight, and styling intent."
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
